            <h1>Summary</h1>
          </section>
          <div id="summary">
            <section>
              <h2>Overview</h2>
              <p>Our team redesigned the moblie application for Access Now. We are hoping the new version of Acess Now
                will benefit more user when looking for a place that is accessible.
              </p>
              <h2>Problem Statement</h2>
              <p>Disable people are facing issue when using the Access Now apps because the apps itself is not
                accessbile enough for them to easily find the information that they are looking for.<span>How might we
                  design a moblie application that helps users to easily look for accessbilty tags and engage with the
                  community.</span></p>
            </section>
            <section style="width: 25%;">
              <h2>Details</h2>
              <h6 class="detailTitle">My Role</h6>
              <h6>Researcher, UX/UI Designer, User-Testing Facilitator, Director</h6>
              <h6 class="detailTitle">The Team</h6>
              <h6>4 UX Designers<br>1 Web Developer</h6>
              <h6 class="detailTitle">Duration</h6>
              <h6>14 Weeks, January - April 2022</h6>
              <h6 class="detailTitle">Project Type</h6>
              <h6>School Project</h6>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
