        <div id="design">
          <section class="title">
            <div class="line"></div>
            <h1>Design Process</h1>
          </section>
          <h3 class="title-highlight">Discovery</h3>
          <h3 class="h3-section">Heuristic Evaluation</h3>
          <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/access/design/herustic.png"
            alt="herustic">
          <h3 class="h3-section">Secondary Reserach Insights & Brainstorm</h3>
          <section id="brainstorm">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/access/design/brainstorm_1.png"
              alt="brainstorm_1">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/access/design/brainstorm_2.png"
              alt="brainstorm_2">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/access/design/brainstorm_3.png"
              alt="brainstorm_3">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/alan-mak/Moonfolio/master/images/access/design/brainstorm_4.png"
              alt="brainstorm_4">
          </section>
          <h3 class="h3-section">Research User Interview</h3>
          <section id="design_points">
            <ul>
              <p>User Pain Points</p>
              <p>Web Developer:</p>
              <li>Outdated information(eg: store location)</li>
              <li>Link that do not have 'title' or 'alt' text</li>
              <p>Content Strategy:</p>
              <li>Tone of voice is informational, not community oriented as it brands itself to be</li>
              <li>Little to no context, pages with "add" and "Profile" have no endpoints</li>
              <p>User Interface / User Experience:</p>
              <li>Unclear instructions</li>
              <li>Lack of graphics</li>
              <li>Imbalanced colour contrast</li>
              <li>Unclear icon legend</li>
            </ul>
            <ul>
              <p>User Needs:</p>
              <li>Clear navigation</li>
              <li>Legible contents and icons </li>
              <li>Clear instruction</li>
              <li>More graphics</li>
              <li>More up-to-date information </li>
              <li>Description text for all links & photos</li>
              <li>To have a fun and friendly community</li>
              <li>To be able to review othersâ€™ comment</li>
              <li>To have a visualized the accessibility </li>tags on the filter page
              <li>To have a balanced colour contrast</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        </div>
